  "desc": "<p>喜歡收集寶物的璃月仙人。太威儀盤的原主人。</p>",
  "iconUrl": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2023/12/20/bcf3c5e99c0f06cc10a700403456164c_8244983452388089599.png",
